        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer628553578" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14508442180292182668">WOW! This historic tale of a doomed arctic expedition set in 1845 aboard the HMS TERROR is based on true events and one horrific adventure complete with unbelievably brutal sub-zero temperatures, and a terrifying <i>monster from hell.</i> Loaded with great characters including the mysterious &apos;Lady Silence&apos; and a unique and surprising ending to say the least. While sometimes descriptively gruesome, an engaging story and thrilling read!</span>
  <span id="freeText14508442180292182668" style="display:none">WOW! This historic tale of a doomed arctic expedition set in 1845 aboard the HMS TERROR is based on true events and one horrific adventure complete with unbelievably brutal sub-zero temperatures, and a terrifying <i>monster from hell.</i> Loaded with great characters including the mysterious 'Lady Silence' and a unique and surprising ending to say the least. While sometimes descriptively gruesome, an engaging story and thrilling read!</span>
