  <span id="freeText14066481815548619788" style="display:none">I'm a big Dan Simmons fan, but at several points during this book, I found myself thinking, "will someone get this man an editor?" <br /><br />There's a great horror tale in here. Unfortunately it's buried under layers of fat. Ironic, since lengthy descriptions of starvation and scurvy take up so much space in the book. <br /><br /></span>
